ce'' (1940)\n|align=\"left\"|{{flagcountry|UKGBI|civil}}\n|align=\"right\"|5,148\n|align=\"left\"|HX\n|align=\"left\"|\n|-\n|align=\"left\"|''Winkleigh'' (1940)\n|align=\"left\"|{{flagcountry|UKGBI|civil}}\n|align=\"right\"|5,468\n|align=\"left\"|BHX 65\n|align=\"left\"|\n|-\n|}\n\n====Escort====\nEscort  information is from Arnold Hague's Convoyweb<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.convoyweb.org.uk/HX/index.html|title=Convoy HX.65|publisher=Arnold Hague Convoy Database|accessdate=4 November 2013}}</ref>\n{|class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|+ Escort ships\n|-\n! scope=\"col\" width=\"150px\"  |Name\n! scope=\"col\" width=\"150px\"  |Flag\n! scope=\"col\" width=\"150px\"   |Ship Type\n! scope=\"col\" width=\"300px\"  |Notes\n|-\n|align=\"left\"|{{HMCS|Assiniboine|I18}}\n|align=\"left\"|{{navy|Canada|1921}}\n|align=\"left\"|[[C and D-class destroyer|C-class]] [[destroyer]]\n|align=\"left\"|Halifax local escort, 12 Aug \u2013 13 Aug\n|-\n|align=\"left\"|HMCS ''French''\n|align=\"left\"|{{navy|Canada|1921}}\n|align=\"left\"| Auxiliary\n|align=\"left\"|Halifax local escort, 12 Aug \u2013 13 Aug\n|-\n|align=\"left\"|{{HMS|Gladiolus|K34}}\n|align=\"left\"|{{navy|UKGBI}}\n|align=\"left\"| [[Flower-class corvette|Flower-class]] [[corvette]]\n|align=\"left\"|Western Approaches escort, 24 Aug \u2013 27 Aug\n|-\n|align=\"left\"|{{HMS|Godetia|K72}}\n|align=\"left\"|{{navy|UKGBI}}\n|align=\"left\"| [[Flower-class corvette|Flower-class]] [[corvette]]\n|align=\"left\"|Western Approaches escort, 22 Aug \u2013 27 Aug\n|-\n|align=\"left\"|{{HMS|Jaguar|F34}}''\n|align=\"left\"|{{navy|UKGBI}}\n|align=\"left\"| [[J-, K- and N-class destroyer|J-class]] [[destroyer]]\n|align=\"left\"|Reinforcement, 26 Aug \u2013 27 Aug\n|-\n|align=\"left\"|{{HMS|Javelin|F61}}''\n|align=\"left\"|{{navy|UKGBI}}\n|align=\"left\"| [[J-, K- and N-class destroyer|J-class]] [[destroyer]]\n|align=\"left\"|Reinforcement, 26 Aug \u2013 27 Aug\n|-\n|align=\"left\"|HMCS ''Laurier''\n|align=\"left\"|{{navy|Canada|1921}}\n|ali