ium Plus cabin starting in August 2020<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://view.ceros.com/united/polaris-tracker-mobile|title=Polaris Tracker - Mobile|website=view.ceros.com|language=en|access-date=2019-04-01}}</ref><br/>One aircraft painted in [[Star Alliance]] livery.\n|-\n|[[Boeing 777|Boeing 777-200]] \n|19\n|&mdash;\n|28\n|&mdash;\n|&mdash;\n|102\n|234\n|364\n|<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.united.com/web/en-US/content/travel/inflight/aircraft/777/200/default.aspx|title=Boeing 777-200 (777) {{!}} United Airlines|website=United.com|language=en-US|accessdate=2017-07-12}}</ref>\n|\n|-\n|rowspan=\"4\"|[[Boeing 777|Boeing 777-200ER]]\n|rowspan=\"4\"|55\n|rowspan=\"4\"|&mdash;\n|32\n| rowspan=\"4\" |&mdash;\n| rowspan=\"3\" |&mdash;\n|124\n|206\n|362\n|<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.united.com/ual/en/us/fly/travel/inflight/aircraft/777-200.html#v6|title=Boeing 777-200 (777) {{!}} United Airlines|website=United.com|language=en-US|accessdate=2020-03-08}}</ref>\n|\n|-\n|48\n|113\n|108\n|269\n|rowspan=\"3\"|<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.united.com/web/en-US/content/travel/inflight/aircraft/777/200/v2.aspx|title=United Airlines - Boeing 777-200 (777) version 2|website=United.com|date=2012-12-14|accessdate=2013-07-09}}</ref>\n| rowspan=\"2\" |To be retrofitted with New Polaris Seats and Premium Plus Cabin on 276 seat-configuration.\n|-\n|rowspan=\"2\"|50\n|72\n|145\n|267\n|-\n|24\n|46\n|156\n|276\n|Five painted in [[Star Alliance]] livery.\n|-\n|[[Boeing 777|Boeing 777-300ER]]\n|22\n|&mdash;\n|60\n|&mdash;\n|24\n|62\n|204\n|350\n|<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.united.com/web/en-US/content/travel/inflight/aircraft/777/300/default.aspx|title=Boeing 777-300ER (77W)}}</ref>\n|\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\" |[[Boeing 787-8]]\n| rowspan=\"2\" |12\n| rowspan=\"2\" |&mdash;\n|28\n| rowspan=\"2\" |&mdash;\n|21\n|36\n|158\n|243\n|<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.united.com/ual/en/us/fly/travel/inflight/aircraft/787-800.html#v2|title=United Airlines - Boeing 787-8 Dreamliner|website=United.com|acce