eing Orders and Deliveries Through April 2018|last=|first=|date=|website=|accessdate=May 8, 2018}}</ref>\n| colspan=\"7\" |<abbr title=\"To be announced\"><center>TBA</center></abbr>\n|Initially planned for service in August 2020 but delayed due to [[Boeing 737 MAX groundings|groundings]].<br>\n<!--------- begin row --------->\n|-\n| rowspan=\"3\" |[[Boeing 757|Boeing 757-200]]\n| rowspan=\"3\" |51\n| rowspan=\"3\" |&mdash;\n| rowspan=\"2\" |16\n| rowspan=\"3\" |&mdash;\n| rowspan=\"3\" |&mdash;\n|45\n|108\n|169\n|<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.united.com/web/en-US/content/travel/inflight/aircraft/757/200/v1.aspx|title=United Airlines - Boeing 757-200 (752) version 1|website=United.com|date=December 14, 2012|accessdate=March 26, 2013}}</ref>\n|Older aircraft to be replaced by the [[Airbus A321XLR]] starting in 2024.\n|-\n|42\n|118\n|176\n|<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.united.com/ual/en/us/fly/travel/inflight/aircraft/757-200.html#v3|title=United Airlines - Boeing 757-200 (752) version 3|last=|first=|date=December 14, 2012|website=United.com|url-status=live|archive-url=|archive-date=|access-date=March 25, 2020}}</ref>\n|One aircraft painted in [[Star Alliance]] livery.<br />One aircraft painted in \u201cNew York-New Jersey\u201d livery.<br>One aircraft painted in \"California\" livery.<!--------- begin row --------->\n|-\n|28\n|42\n|72\n|142\n|<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.united.com/web/en-US/content/travel/inflight/aircraft/757/200/v2.aspx|title=United Airlines - Boeing 757-200 (752) version 2|last=|first=|date=December 14, 2012|website=United.com|url-status=live|archive-url=|archive-date=|accessdate=March 26, 2013}}</ref>\n|Premium Transcontinental Service configuration.<br>\n|-\n|[[Boeing 757|Boeing 757-300]]\n|21\n|&mdash;\n|&mdash;\n|24\n|&mdash;\n|54\n|156\n|234\n|<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.united.com/web/en-US/content/travel/inflight/aircraft/757/300/default.aspx|title=United Airlines - Boeing 757-300 (753)|date=September 25, 2019|website=United.com|u